  <title>GLib.OptionGroup.prototype.set_translate_func</title>
  <synopsis><code mime="text/x-gjs">
function set_translate_func(func: <link xref="GLib.TranslateFunc">GLib.TranslateFunc</link>): void {
    // Gjs wrapper for g_option_group_set_translate_func()
}
  </code></synopsis>
  <p>Sets the function which is used to translate user-visible strings,
for `--help` output. Different groups can use different
#GTranslateFuncs. If <code>func</code> is <code>null</code>, strings are not translated.</p>  <p>If you are using gettext(), you only need to set the translation
domain, see <link xref="GLib.set_translation_domain"/>.</p>
  <p>Since 2.6</p>
